</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="navbar-container">
            <a href="#" class="navbar-brand" data-page="home"><span></span>Neumorph</a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button">
                <div style="width: 25px; height: 3px; background: var(--accent-color); margin: 5px 0;"></div>
                <div style="width: 25px; height: 3px; background: var(--accent-color); margin: 5px 0;"></div>
                <div style="width: 25px; height: 3px; background: var(--accent-color); margin: 5px 0;"></div>
            </button>
            <div class="navbar-collapse" id="navbarContent">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a href="#" class="nav-link active" data-page="home">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a href="#" class="nav-link" data-page="features">Features</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a href="#" class="nav-link" data-page="about">About</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a href="#" class="nav-link" data-page="contact">Contact</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="navbar-form">
                    <div class="user-profile" id="userProfileSection" style="display: none;">
                        <div class="user-avatar" id="userAvatar">JS</div>
                        <div class="dropdown-menu" id="userDropdown">
                            <a href="#" class="dropdown-item"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> Profile</a>
                            <a href="#" class="dropdown-item"><i class="fas fa-cog"></i> Settings</a>
                            <div class="dropdown-divider"></div>
                            <a href="#" class="dropdown-item" id="logoutBtn"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Logout</a>
                        </div>
    
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-section" id="home-section">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Neumorphic Layout Example</h1>
                <p>A modern and elegant soft interface design that brings dimension to flat surfaces</p>
                <div class="feature-badge">Clean Design</div>
                <div class="feature-badge">Soft UI</div>
                <div class="feature-badge">Minimal</div>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <div class="card">
                    <h2>Designer Cards</h2>
                    <p>Elevated cards with subtle shadows create a clean, modern look while maintaining a soft appearance. Hover over to see the animation effect.</p>
                    <div class="inset">
                        <p>This inset element appears to be pressed into the surface, creating visual depth.</p>
                    </div>
                    <button class="button" data-page="features">Learn More</button>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h2>Smart Inputs</h2>
                    <p>Neumorphism combines flat design with subtle shadows to create a soft UI that looks extruded from the background.</p>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="text" class="input" placeholder="Username">
                    </div>
                    <label class="toggle-switch">
                        <input type="checkbox" checked>
                        <span class="toggle-slider"></span>
                    </label>
                    <button class="button outline" data-page="contact">Submit</button>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h2>Depth Effects</h2>
                    <p>Notice how the elements appear to be carved out of a single material, with soft shadows giving depth without harsh contrasts.</p>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <p>Perfect for dashboards, mobile apps, and modern web interfaces that need a touch of elegance.</p>
                    <button class="button" data-page="about">Explore More</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section" id="features-section">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Features</h1>
                <p>Discover the powerful features of our neumorphic design system</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <div class="card">
                    <h2>Responsive Design</h2>
                    <p>Fully responsive layouts that work beautifully on all devices, from mobile phones to desktop computers.</p>
                    <div class="inset">
                        <p>Adaptive components automatically adjust to different screen sizes.</p>
                    </div>
                    <button class="button" data-page="home">Back to Home</button>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h2>Interactive Elements</h2>
                    <p>Carefully crafted buttons, inputs, and toggles that respond to user interaction with subtle animations.</p>
                    <div class="toggle-switch">
                        <input type="checkbox" checked>
                        <span class="toggle-slider"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="toggle-switch">
                        <input type="checkbox">
                        <span class="toggle-slider"></span>
                    </div>
                    <button class="button outline" id="try-button">Try It</button>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h2>Consistent Design Language</h2>
                    <p>A unified design system that maintains visual consistency across all UI components.</p>
                    <div class="feature-badge">Components</div>
                    <div class="feature-badge">Typography</div>
                    <div class="feature-badge">Colors</div>
                    <div class="feature-badge">Spacing</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section" id="about-section">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>About Neumorphism</h1>
                <p>The evolution of UI design that brings depth to digital interfaces</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <div class="card">
                    <h2>What is Neumorphism?</h2>
                    <p>Neumorphism (or Neo-skeuomorphism) is a design trend that combines elements of skeuomorphism and flat design. It uses subtle shadow techniques to create UI elements that appear to extrude from or be pressed into the background.</p>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                    <p>The term was coined in late 2019 and has gained popularity for its soft, minimal aesthetic that provides a sense of depth without excessive visual noise.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h2>Design Principles</h2>
                    <p>Key characteristics of neumorphic design include:</p>
                    <div class="inset">
                        <p>• Monochromatic color schemes</p>
                        <p>• Subtle shadow contrasts</p>
                        <p>• Soft, extruded appearance</p>
                        <p>• Minimal highlights</p>
                    </div>
                    <button class="button" data-page="home">Back to Home</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-section" id="contact-section">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Contact Us</h1>
                <p>Get in touch with our team for any questions or feedback</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <div class="card">
                    <h2>Send a Message</h2>
                    <form id="contact-form">
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="text" class="input" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <input type="email" class="input" placeholder="Your Email" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="inset" style="padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                            <textarea id="message-area" style="width: 100%; min-height: 120px; background: transparent; border: none; resize: vertical; outline: none;" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="button">Send Message</button>
                    </form>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <h2>Connect With Us</h2>
                    <p>Follow us on social media or reach out directly.</p>
                    <div class="social-icons">
                        <div class="social-icon" data-icon="f">f</div>
                        <div class="social-icon" data-icon="in">in</div>
                        <div class="social-icon" data-icon="t">t</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer>
            <p>Neumorphic Layout Example &copy; 2025</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="authButtons">
                        <button type="button" class="btn-search" id="loginBtn">Login</button>
                        <button type="button" class="btn-search" id="signupBtn" style="margin-left: 10px; background: var(--background); color: var(--accent-color);">Sign up</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    
    <!-- Login/Signup Modal -->
    <div class="modal-overlay" id="authModal">
        <div class="modal-container">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h2 id="modalTitle">Login</h2>
                <button class="modal-close" id="closeModal">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="tab-navigation">
                    <button class="tab-button active" id="loginTab">Login</button>
                    <button class="tab-button" id="signupTab">Sign up</button>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tab-content active" id="loginContent">
                    <form id="loginForm">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Email</label>
                            <div class="form-control-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                                <input type="email" class="form-control-auth" placeholder="Your email" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Password</label>
                            <div class="form-control-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                                <input type="password" class="form-control-auth" placeholder="Your password" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-remember">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="rememberMe">
                            <label for="rememberMe">Remember me</label>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-auth">Login</button>
                    </form>
                    
                    <div class="auth-separator">
                        <span>or login with</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="social-auth">
                        <button class="social-auth-btn" title="Google"><i class="fab fa-google"></i></button>
                        <button class="social-auth-btn" title="Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></button>
                        <button class="social-auth-btn" title="Twitter"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></button>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="auth-footer">
                        <p>Don't have an account? <a href="#" id="switchToSignup">Sign up</a></p>
                        <p style="margin-top: 10px;"><a href="#">Forgot password?</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="tab-content" id="signupContent">
                    <form id="signupForm">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Full Name</label>
                            <div class="form-control-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control-auth" placeholder="Your full name" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Email</label>
                            <div class="form-control-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                                <input type="email" class="form-control-auth" placeholder="Your email" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Password</label>
                            <div class="form-control-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                                <input type="password" class="form-control-auth" placeholder="Create password" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label class="form-label">Confirm Password</label>
                            <div class="form-control-icon">
                                <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                                <input type="password" class="form-control-auth" placeholder="Confirm password" required>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-remember">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="agreeTerms" required>
                            <label for="agreeTerms">I agree to the <a href="#">Terms of Service</a></label>
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn-auth">Create Account</button>
                    </form>
                    
                    <div class="auth-separator">
                        <span>or sign up with</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="social-auth">
                        <button class="social-auth-btn" title="Google"><i class="fab fa-google"></i></button>
                        <button class="social-auth-btn" title="Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></button>
                        <button class="social-auth-btn" title="Twitter"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></button>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="auth-footer">
                        <p>Already have an account? <a href="#" id="switchToLogin">Login</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="./scripts/home.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
        

